title: Its Our Anniversary
itunes:title: Its Our Anniversary
description:
Its our 9 year anniversary today!! So in celebration of our anniversary we had our listeners call up and tell us their favorite Breakfast Club moments. Moreover we also had Fat Joe and Dre from Cool and Dre where they stopped by to promote their album, Fat Joe possibly retiring and more. Also, Charlamagne decided to give us a little background of where the sound bytes for his Donkey of the Day intros came from.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
